DarkMouse::

She looked up at Apocalypse. She wondered why she was such a big 
deal.  She was only a mouse. But a mouse that could heal from masive 
wounds in minutes and hack into any predacon or maximal computer.

She smiled slightly. She was going to need protection if she was 
going to survive this time.
